sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant S as Resource Server

    C->>G: POST /login (credentials)
    activate G
    G->>A: Validate credentials
    activate A
    A-->>G: JWT token
    deactivate A
    G-->>C: 200 OK + token
    deactivate G

    C->>G: GET /api/data (Bearer token)
    activate G
    G->>A: Verify token
    A-->>G: Valid
    G->>S: Forward request
    activate S
    S-->>G: Response data
    deactivate S
    G-->>C: 200 OK + data
    deactivate G
